%section
  %h3 Melbourne Ruby

  %article
    %h4 When
    %p Melbourne Ruby meetings happen on the last Wednesday of every month (with the exception of December which has a social event sometime in the middle of the month).

    %p Melbourne Ruby hack nights (where the focus is more on coding than talking) happen on the second Wednesday of every month.

    %p All events are listed on <a href="http://www.meetup.com/Ruby-On-Rails-Oceania-Melbourne/">Meetup.com</a>.

  %article
